      • assignLabels

        protected void assignLabels(VCard vcard,
                List<Label> labels)
        Matches up a list of Label properties with their corresponding Address properties. If no match can be found, then the LABEL property itself is assigned to the vCard.
        Parameters:
        vcard - the vCard that the properties belong to
        labels - the LABEL properties
